[
    {
        "text": "In the late 17th century, a medical student named Johannes Hofer...",
        "startTime": 271,
        "endTime": 4037,
        "slowStartTime": 556,
        "slowEndTime": 6281
    },
    {
        "text": "...noticed a strange illness affecting Swiss mercenaries serving abroad.",
        "startTime": 4277,
        "endTime": 8907,
        "slowStartTime": 6565,
        "slowEndTime": 13586
    },
    {
        "text": "Its symptoms, including fatigue, insomnia, irregular heartbeat, indigestion,...",
        "startTime": 9457,
        "endTime": 14979,
        "slowStartTime": 14335,
        "slowEndTime": 22694
    },
    {
        "text": "...and fever were so strong, the soldiers often had to be discharged.",
        "startTime": 15245,
        "endTime": 19808,
        "slowStartTime": 23017,
        "slowEndTime": 29937
    },
    {
        "text": "As Hofer discovered, the cause was not some physical disturbance,...",
        "startTime": 20428,
        "endTime": 24217,
        "slowStartTime": 30792,
        "slowEndTime": 36551
    },
    {
        "text": "...but an intense yearning for their mountain homeland.",
        "startTime": 24457,
        "endTime": 27255,
        "slowStartTime": 36836,
        "slowEndTime": 41108
    },
    {
        "text": "He dubbed the condition \"nostalgia,\"...",
        "startTime": 28000,
        "endTime": 30118,
        "slowStartTime": 42150,
        "slowEndTime": 45402
    },
    {
        "text": "...from the Greek \"nostos\" for homecoming and \"algos\" for pain or longing.",
        "startTime": 30355,
        "endTime": 35289,
        "slowStartTime": 45682,
        "slowEndTime": 53159
    },
    {
        "text": "At first, nostalgia was considered a particularly Swiss affliction.",
        "startTime": 35917,
        "endTime": 40241,
        "slowStartTime": 54025,
        "slowEndTime": 60587
    },
    {
        "text": "Some doctors proposed that the constant sound of cowbells in the Alps...",
        "startTime": 40725,
        "endTime": 45071,
        "slowStartTime": 61237,
        "slowEndTime": 67831
    },
    {
        "text": "...caused trauma to the eardrums and brain.",
        "startTime": 45297,
        "endTime": 48281,
        "slowStartTime": 68096,
        "slowEndTime": 72647
    },
    {
        "text": "Commanders even forbade their soldiers from singing traditional Swiss songs...",
        "startTime": 49081,
        "endTime": 53551,
        "slowStartTime": 73771,
        "slowEndTime": 80551
    },
    {
        "text": "...for fear that they'd lead to desertion or suicide.",
        "startTime": 53854,
        "endTime": 56869,
        "slowStartTime": 80931,
        "slowEndTime": 85528
    },
    {
        "text": "But as migration increased worldwide, nostalgia was observed in various groups.",
        "startTime": 57950,
        "endTime": 63163,
        "slowStartTime": 87075,
        "slowEndTime": 94970
    },
    {
        "text": "It turned out that anyone separated from their native place for a long time...",
        "startTime": 63669,
        "endTime": 68202,
        "slowStartTime": 95654,
        "slowEndTime": 102528
    },
    {
        "text": "...was vulnerable to nostalgia.",
        "startTime": 68457,
        "endTime": 70203,
        "slowStartTime": 102836,
        "slowEndTime": 105529
    },
    {
        "text": "And by the early 20th century,...",
        "startTime": 70675,
        "endTime": 72359,
        "slowStartTime": 106163,
        "slowEndTime": 108764
    },
    {
        "text": "...professionals no longer viewed it as a neurological disease,...",
        "startTime": 72564,
        "endTime": 76229,
        "slowStartTime": 108996,
        "slowEndTime": 114569
    },
    {
        "text": "...but as a mental condition similar to depression.",
        "startTime": 76423,
        "endTime": 79035,
        "slowStartTime": 114784,
        "slowEndTime": 118778
    },
    {
        "text": "Psychologists of the time speculated...",
        "startTime": 79551,
        "endTime": 81521,
        "slowStartTime": 119477,
        "slowEndTime": 122507
    },
    {
        "text": "...that it represented difficulties letting go of childhood,...",
        "startTime": 81597,
        "endTime": 84983,
        "slowStartTime": 122545,
        "slowEndTime": 127700
    },
    {
        "text": "...or even a longing to return to one's fetal state.",
        "startTime": 85382,
        "endTime": 88304,
        "slowStartTime": 128223,
        "slowEndTime": 132681
    }
]